- **Project Vision:** [Review EnginUp South Concept](mdc:path/to/your/concept-document.txt) - Empower South Indian engineering students with AI-driven career prep and skill-building.
- **Development Workflow:** Follow the [dev_workflow.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/dev_workflow.mdc) guide for task management (`task-master` commands).
    - Use `task-master parse-prd` on the concept doc initially.
    - Break down features (Resume Builder, Portfolio Gen, etc.) into detailed tasks using `task-master expand`.
    - Prioritize Phase 1 MVP features.
- **Core Technologies (Initial Choices - Adapt as needed):**
    - **Frontend:** React ([enginup-frontend.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/enginup-frontend.mdc))
    - **Backend:** Python/Flask or Node.js/Express ([enginup-backend.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/enginup-backend.mdc)) - Decide based on team expertise & AI library preference.
    - **Database:** PostgreSQL (Consider creating `enginup-db.mdc` for database guidelines)
    - **AI Integration:** Primarily API-based initially ([enginup-ai.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/enginup-ai.mdc))
    - **Hosting:** Cloud Platform (AWS/GCP/Azure)
- **Regionalization Strategy:** ([enginup-regionalization.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/enginup-regionalization.mdc))
    - Prioritize South India focus in content (jobs, companies, skills).
    - Plan for multi-language UI/support later.
